data.description: Beautifully updated home on a large corner lot awaits its new owner.  Once you walk in to the living area you will feel at home. The large new  windows lets the light in and the all new kitchen with new gas stove, refrigerator and dishwasher is inviting to cook your next meal. The brand new white cabinets and new counter tops finish this beautiful kitchen. The main level also has 2 large bedrooms with new carpet and the bathroom has been updated with modern tile, sink and tub. Down stairs in the basement you will find new laminate flooring through out, the large laundry room at the bottom of the stairs which flows into the family room. Two more large bedrooms that have updated paint, laminate flooring and new windows await there occupants with anticipation. Another bathroom with a shower makes it a finished space. The garage has a walkway from the basement up to the garage, making it actually attached so you are not walking in the snow, but from outside looks detached. The garage is a large 2 car garage and the other side of the home boast a long driveway to park the rest of your toys.  The neighborhood is off 18th street, away from the hustle of the main streets and makes for quiet evenings and a great place to go home to. Call today for your private showing.
